You also might want to include STUN as a spell that also compliments an enchanter. The others (Force etc cause damage that can disrupt the enchanters spells, so avoid them if you can)<P>Good Post Labyrrinth,<BR>I group with an enchantress and I always make her the priority for heals, also if you're grouped with Paladins or Rangers, ask them to keep an eye on the enchanters health. Granted that they can't heal as much as Clerics can, but sometimes its enough. And yes sometimes 3 various heal spells go off on the enchanter, but then as you said... dead enchanter = dead cleric = dead party (unless they run real real fast)<P>Durus
