<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Well, I certainly make the enchanters my priority target for heals...<P>BUT<P>When I've played my warrior my group has often survived after the enchanter bit the dust.  Enchanters are a convenience, and we hate losing them..but non caster mobs can be root parked or your main tank can keep all the mobs agro'd on him while the rest of the group eliminates one mob at a time.<P>My warrior spent from level 35 to level 50 doing lower guk and sol b and was grouped with enchanters only about a half dozen times, and we survived multiple mob pulls just fine.  I remember one memorable time doing the Frenzy without even a cleric..just had a very good 49 necro that used pact of shadows and kept me alive.  Of course your tanks have to know what they're doing and how to trade off agro with each other in order to get maximum benefit of the group memmbers hit points.
</FONT>
