Not to go against the collected wisdom of the previous posts, but I rarely if ever would choose to heal the chanter first.  The reasons are as follows:<BR>1) The back up healer should take care of casters, who have fewer hitpoints and lesser heals are generally sufficient<BR>2) In the scenerio mentioned - what if the warrior died because I was wasting my time healing a pure caster?  Yes, I can see it now, Icewind the mad cleric meleer... it's a surer sign of death than anything else.<BR>*** As an aside, I usually group with a Pally, a Druidess, a Chanter, a Wizard and Mage.. so please realize that under other circumstances, my choice of who to heal might change.
